    {
      "paragraph_name": "COPAU1A",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This DFHMDI macro defines the map COPAU1A, which represents the screen layout within the COPAU01 mapset. It sets the screen size to 24 lines by 80 columns (SIZE=(24,80)) and positions the map at the top-left corner of the screen (COLUMN=1, LINE=1). This macro acts as a container for the individual fields defined by DFHMDF macros, arranging them on the screen. It defines the overall dimensions and placement of the screen elements that make up the 'View Authorization Details' display.",
